## Path Traversal Attack Playbook

> **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like `{FILE_PATH}`, `{DEPTH}`, `{TARGET_FILE}` with actual values. Adapt payloads based on:
