# Objective and context
Write and execute a Python script to perform UNION-based SQL injection enumeration on send.php (http://127.0.0.1:32826/send.php) to discover table names and columns. 

The script should:
1. Test each parameter (fullname, email, phone, subject, message) individually for UNION-based SQL injection
